{"title":"CF1175B-Catch Overflow","uid":"1546dd1809f28cdefc1c0a246e183f01","slug":"CF1175B","date":"2021-08-10T05:18:36.000Z","updated":"2021-08-11T08:29:04.490Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/CF1175B.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>用到栈的模拟题~</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h3 id=\"题意概括\"><a href=\"#题意概括\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题意概括\"></a>题意概括</h3><p>有初始值a=0，进行x次操作，共有如下三种操作模式：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>add：使a增加1</li>\n<li>for num：将其和与之适配的end之间所有操作循环执行num次</li>\n<li>end：与for适配</li>\n</ul>\n<p>如果a的值大于<mjx-container class=\"MathJax\" jax=\"SVG\"><svg style=\"vertical-align: 0;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"2.919ex\" height=\"1.887ex\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" viewBox=\"0 -833.9 1290.1 833.9\"><g stroke=\"currentColor\" fill=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"0\" transform=\"scale(1,-1)\"><g data-mml-node=\"math\"><g data-mml-node=\"msup\"><g data-mml-node=\"mn\"><path data-c=\"32\" d=\"M109 429Q82 429 66 447T50 491Q50 562 103 614T235 666Q326 666 387 610T449 465Q449 422 429 383T381 315T301 241Q265 210 201 149L142 93L218 92Q375 92 385 97Q392 99 409 186V189H449V186Q448 183 436 95T421 3V0H50V19V31Q50 38 56 46T86 81Q115 113 136 137Q145 147 170 174T204 211T233 244T261 278T284 308T305 340T320 369T333 401T340 431T343 464Q343 527 309 573T212 619Q179 619 154 602T119 569T109 550Q109 549 114 549Q132 549 151 535T170 489Q170 464 154 447T109 429Z\"></path></g><g data-mml-node=\"TeXAtom\" transform=\"translate(533,363) scale(0.707)\" data-mjx-texclass=\"ORD\"><g data-mml-node=\"mn\"><path data-c=\"33\" d=\"M127 463Q100 463 85 480T69 524Q69 579 117 622T233 665Q268 665 277 664Q351 652 390 611T430 522Q430 470 396 421T302 350L299 348Q299 347 308 345T337 336T375 315Q457 262 457 175Q457 96 395 37T238 -22Q158 -22 100 21T42 130Q42 158 60 175T105 193Q133 193 151 175T169 130Q169 119 166 110T159 94T148 82T136 74T126 70T118 67L114 66Q165 21 238 21Q293 21 321 74Q338 107 338 175V195Q338 290 274 322Q259 328 213 329L171 330L168 332Q166 335 166 348Q166 366 174 366Q202 366 232 371Q266 376 294 413T322 525V533Q322 590 287 612Q265 626 240 626Q208 626 181 615T143 592T132 580H135Q138 579 143 578T153 573T165 566T175 555T183 540T186 520Q186 498 172 481T127 463Z\"></path><path data-c=\"32\" d=\"M109 429Q82 429 66 447T50 491Q50 562 103 614T235 666Q326 666 387 610T449 465Q449 422 429 383T381 315T301 241Q265 210 201 149L142 93L218 92Q375 92 385 97Q392 99 409 186V189H449V186Q448 183 436 95T421 3V0H50V19V31Q50 38 56 46T86 81Q115 113 136 137Q145 147 170 174T204 211T233 244T261 278T284 308T305 340T320 369T333 401T340 431T343 464Q343 527 309 573T212 619Q179 619 154 602T119 569T109 550Q109 549 114 549Q132 549 151 535T170 489Q170 464 154 447T109 429Z\" transform=\"translate(500,0)\"></path></g></g></g></g></g></svg></mjx-container>，输出**OVERFLOW!!!**，否则输出a。</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目分析\"><a href=\"#题目分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目分析\"></a>题目分析</h3><p>没啥好说的模拟-.-</p>\n<p>坑点：for循环经过多次堆叠后每次add操作的值有可能大于longlong范围，当然也有可能多次堆叠后不进行add操作，使得堆叠的值又慢慢变小，因此我们可以利用栈存储堆叠到当前状态下需要循环的总次数，而非单次循环的次数。</p>\n<h3 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;\n#define int long long\nusing namespace std;\nint n, now;\nstack&lt;int&gt; st;\n\nsigned main() {\n\tios::sync_with_stdio(false);\n\tint loop = pow(2, 32);\n\tcin &gt;&gt; n;\n\tst.push(1);\n\twhile (n--) {\n\t\tstring command;\n\t\tcin &gt;&gt; command;\n\t\tif (command == \"add\") {\n\t\t\tnow += st.top();\n\t\t\tif (now &gt;= loop) {\n\t\t\t\tputs(\"OVERFLOW!!!\");\n\t\t\t\treturn 0;\n\t\t\t}\n\t\t} else if (command == \"for\") {\n\t\t\tint temp;\n\t\t\tcin &gt;&gt; temp;\n\t\t\tif (temp == 0)\n\t\t\t\tcontinue;\n\t\t\tst.push(min(st.top()*temp, loop));\n\t\t} else {\n\t\t\tif (st.empty())\n\t\t\t\tcontinue;\n\t\t\tint temp = st.top();\n\t\t\tst.pop();\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tcout &lt;&lt; now &lt;&lt; endl;\n\treturn 0;\n}</code></pre>\n\n","text":"用到栈的模拟题~ 题意概括有初始值a=0，进行x次操作，共有如下三种操作模式： add：使a增加1 for num：将其和与之适配的end之间所有操作循环执行num次 end：与for适配 如果a的值大于，输出**OVERFLOW!!!**，否则输出a。 题目分析没啥好说的模拟-...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":914,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":33,"path":"api/categories/题解.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CodeForces","slug":"CodeForces","count":13,"path":"api/tags/CodeForces.json"},{"name":"恢复OI实力","slug":"恢复OI实力","count":23,"path":"api/tags/恢复OI实力.json"},{"name":"模拟","slug":"模拟","count":5,"path":"api/tags/模拟.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E6%84%8F%E6%A6%82%E6%8B%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题意概括</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90\"><span class=\"toc-text\">题目分析</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"白泽","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"一个正在追逐游戏开发梦的大学生！","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/svg/Bilibili.svg","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/91730547"},"zhihu":{"icon":"/svg/Zhihu.svg","link":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/ying-zong-pai-wu-seng"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"HDU2197-本源串","uid":"db16d1c3f4775338fc6ee6b9aaac01fc","slug":"HDU2197","date":"2021-08-11T06:18:24.000Z","updated":"2021-08-15T07:40:39.521Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HDU2197.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"简单的递归处理，或者说是思维题？ 题意概括由0和1组成的串中，不能表示为由几个相同的较小的串连接成的串，称为本原串，有多少个长为n（n&lt;=100000000)的本原串？答案mod2008。例如，100100不是本原串，因为他是由两个100组成，而1101是本原串。 题目分析...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.1k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"题解","slug":"题解","count":33,"path":"api/categori